RUN /bin/sh -c set -eux; 		wget -O python.tar.xz "https://www.python.org/ftp/python/${PYTHON_VERSION%%[a-z]*}/Python-$PYTHON_VERSION.tar.xz"; 	echo "$PYTHON_SHA256 *python.tar.xz" | sha256sum -c -; 	wget -O python.tar.xz.asc "https://www.python.org/ftp/python/${PYTHON_VERSION%%[a-z]*}/Python-$PYTHON_VERSION.tar.xz.asc"; 	GNUPGHOME="$(mktemp -d)"; export GNUPGHOME; 	gpg --batch --keyserver hkps://keys.openpgp.org --recv-keys "$GPG_KEY"; 	gpg --batch --verify python.tar.xz.asc python.tar.xz; 	gpgconf --kill all; 	rm -rf "$GNUPGHOME" python.tar.xz.asc; 	./configure 		--build="$gnuArch" 		--enable-loadable-sqlite-extensions 		--enable-optimizations 		--enable-option-checking=fatal 		--enable-shared 		--with-lto 		--with-ensurepip 	; 	nproc="$(nproc)";
